+### Directory Breakdown
+
+- `app/`: Core Next.js application directory using App Router
+  - Contains page components, layouts, and route-specific logic
+- `public/`: Static assets accessible directly via web paths
+- `scripts/`: Utility and build-related scripts
+- `styles/`: Global styling and Tailwind configuration
+- `types/`: TypeScript type definitions for the project
+
+#### Key Configuration Files
+- `next.config.js`: Next.js project configuration
+- `tailwind.config.js`: Tailwind CSS customization
+- `tsconfig.json`: TypeScript compiler settings
